                    <comment id="12609161" author="larsko" created="Mon, 30 Jun 2008 07:23:16 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch changing &quot;text.length()&amp;lt; maxDocCharsToAnalyze&quot; to &quot;text.length()&amp;lt;= maxDocCharsToAnalyze&quot; and adding a unit test to verify this behaviour.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                    <comment id="12609220" author="markrmiller@gmail.com" created="Mon, 30 Jun 2008 13:34:22 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks Lars. Nice catch - not an easy spot &amp;lt;g&amp;gt; Looks good to me. When I get a few free minutes I&apos;ll go over it a bit more, but on first inspection, certainly looks like the right fix and all tests pass.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
